subject: College Athletics
Basketball
NCAA Basketball Tournament
lead_paragraph: Andy Rautins tied a team record with nine 3-pointers and scored a career-high 29 points to lead No. 17 Syracuse to an 82-71 victory over visiting Coppin State on Monday night.
